    "contentHtml": "<div align=\"center\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: teal;\" class=\"bbc_color\">GMK CYL Windbreaker</span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 30pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">GB Live Until November 9th!</span></span><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/snKVhVp.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/snKVhVp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br />It&#039;s here folks. After 3 years, it&#039;s finally time for GMK CYL Windbreaker. Sorry I&#039;ve made you wait longer than I should have, but thank you for your patience, and I hope you enjoy the set. I&#039;ve made you wait long enough, so on with the show!<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Kits</span></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: orange;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Base</span></span><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WWNHAxn.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WWNHAxn.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br />A phat base kit for almost everything you could need to cover: TKL, 65%, 60%, Alice, 4-key 40%, HHKB and more!<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: orange;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Novelties</span></span><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1SpbmMX.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1SpbmMX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br />Some choice novelties referencing some of your fave goodies of the past, also features orange gamer WASD.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: orange;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Numpad</span></span><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/OOIo3ms.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OOIo3ms.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br />Wanna crunch some numbers? Here you go. <br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: orange;\" class=\"bbc_color\">International</span></span><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dEnDsDq.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dEnDsDq.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br />A little something something for my ISO friends. <br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Pricing</span></span><br /><br />US Pricing<br /><br />Base: $135<br />Novelties: $45<br />Numpad: $35<br />International: $65<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Vendors</span></span><br /><br />Worldwide: <a href=\"https://prototypist.net/products/group-buy-gmk-cyl-windbreaker\" class=\"bbc_link\" target=\"_blank\">Proto[Typist]</a><br />US: <a href=\"https://novelkeys.com/products/gmk-cyl-windbreaker-keycaps\" class=\"bbc_link\" target=\"_blank\">Novelkeys</a><br />EU: Oblotzky Industries<br />KR: Geon<br />CN: Typist Club<br />SEA: <a href=\"https://ilumkb.com/products/group-buy-gmk-cyl-windbreaker\" class=\"bbc_link\" target=\"_blank\">iLumKB</a><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Renders</span></span><br /><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IiQ9Xtd.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IiQ9Xtd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fl1Hg8H.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fl1Hg8H.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/vrPPxog.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vrPPxog.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TiTAHKF.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TiTAHKF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/6rtvxtF.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6rtvxtF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5NL43pa.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5NL43pa.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/snKVhVp.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/snKVhVp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ck2ZfTt.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ck2ZfTt.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/o3XPPa4.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o3XPPa4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><a  href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XqBzEzx.jpeg\" class=\"highslide \" onclick=\"return hs.expand(this, { slideshowGroup: '3210618' })\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XqBzEzx.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" align=\"\" class=\"bbc_img\" /></a><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Colors</span></span><br /><br />GMK will be sent references from DCS Windbreaker for colormatching purposes.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Details</span></span><br /><br />GB runs from October 10th 2025 to November 9th 2025. <br /><br />Cherry Profile, ABS, Doubleshot, MX compatible, 112344 row sculpt, manufactured by GMK, you know the drill folks. <br /><br />Estimated Shipping: Q1-Q2 2026<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36pt;\" class=\"bbc_size\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\" class=\"bbc_color\">Thanks</span></span><br /><br />Thank you to everyone who helped get me off my ass and work on this, thanks to everyone who kept asking for this over the last few years, and thanks to all of you who helped make the original DCS Windbreaker a reality. <br /><br />Who would have thought an April Fools joke could go on this long? <br /><br />Join <a href=\"https://discord.gg/7DjS5Bt\" class=\"bbc_link\" target=\"_blank\">My Discord</a> or follow me on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/philippwade/\" class=\"bbc_link\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> if you&#039;re into that sort of thing.<br /><br />Thanks for looking <3<br /><br /></div></div>",
    "contentText": "GMK CYL Windbreaker\nGB Live Until November 9th!\nIt&#039;s here folks. After 3 years, it&#039;s finally time for GMK CYL Windbreaker. Sorry I&#039;ve made you wait longer than I should have, but thank you for your patience, and I hope you enjoy the set. I&#039;ve made you wait long enough, so on with the show!\nKits\nBase\nA phat base kit for almost everything you could need to cover: TKL, 65%, 60%, Alice, 4-key 40%, HHKB and more!\nNovelties\nSome choice novelties referencing some of your fave goodies of the past, also features orange gamer WASD.\nNumpad\nWanna crunch some numbers? Here you go.\nInternational\nA little something something for my ISO friends.\nPricing\nUS Pricing\nBase: $135\nNovelties: $45\nNumpad: $35\nInternational: $65\nVendors\nWorldwide: Proto[Typist]\nUS: Novelkeys\nEU: Oblotzky Industries\nKR: Geon\nCN: Typist Club\nSEA: iLumKB\nRenders\nColors\nGMK will be sent references from DCS Windbreaker for colormatching purposes.\nDetails\nGB runs from October 10th 2025 to November 9th 2025.\nCherry Profile, ABS, Doubleshot, MX compatible, 112344 row sculpt, manufactured by GMK, you know the drill folks.\nEstimated Shipping: Q1-Q2 2026\nThanks\nThank you to everyone who helped get me off my ass and work on this, thanks to everyone who kept asking for this over the last few years, and thanks to all of you who helped make the original DCS Windbreaker a reality.\nWho would have thought an April Fools joke could go on this long?\nJoin My Discord or follow me on Instagram if you&#039;re into that sort of thing.\nThanks for looking",
